      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precision-engineered 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains balanced with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup, currently fitted with Bilstein dampers for enhanced damping control. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a crisp exhaust note through the quad-exit system.",
